
查會員 2 個月內未出席
查詢：
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM classRecord WHERE bookinDate < '2025-02-03 00:00:00' AND memberId = 105 AND status = 1 (代表未出席)

建立索引：
CREATE INDEX IX_classRecord_memberId_bookinDate_status ON classRecord (memberId, bookinDate, status);

－－－－－

查某課程的預約人數
查詢：
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM classRecord WHERE groupClassScheduleId = 10 AND status = 1 (此課程未上, 所以代表 總預約人數)
建立索引：
CREATE INDEX IX_classRecord_groupClassScheduleId_status ON classRecord (groupClassScheduleId, status);